{"tid":762062,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【吳雨幾時收皮】《今晚見》玩完！朱慧珊、梁思浩對撼《東張西望》","createTime":"2018-07-31T02:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T03:49:44.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7a629d61e962b7baa96612576cb82642943cfa0","tid":762062,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"《今晚見》玩完！朱慧珊梁思浩對撼《東張》<br />\n07月31日(二) 00:00  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180731/photo/bkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_04p.jpg?20180731034302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180731%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20180731034302&h=aa64c3f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來係咁！梁思浩與朱慧珊將會主持時事娛樂節目《香港追擊》。<br />\n <br />\n亞視屢傳財困，有爆料指娛樂節目《今晚見》因而停播，但亞視外事部總監曾醒明回覆稱：「《今》於7月完結係規劃之內，9月將有全新節目出街，證明冇財困亦冇裁員！」而首席內容官何麗全透露，9月將推出時事娛樂節目《香港追擊》，形式類似當年亞視皇牌節目《今日睇真D》，這個一星期播五日的半小時節目，將對撼無綫《東張西望》，主持方面由朱慧珊和梁思浩主持，並會羅致不少前無綫新聞主播如周嘉儀和伍家謙等加盟，以壯聲勢。伍家謙受訪坦言：「如果時間配合到會考慮嘅！」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180731/photo/bkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_05p.jpg?20180731034302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180731%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20180731034302&h=2b41a6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n形式似當年亞視皇牌節目《今日睇真D》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180731/photo/bkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_06p.jpg?20180731034302\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180731%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20180731034302&h=735f0ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲會搵前無綫新聞主播周嘉儀加盟。<br />\n<br />\n轉自東方日報網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180731/mobile/bkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180731%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001.html&d=ZwXxiz8aJHjnUpSvs3T%2F7jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=02ff193b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180731/mobile/bkn-20180731000019531-0731_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9605a1a86a8e2164e2f7e3305bd2dc7b25bf2253","tid":762062,"uid":1848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"首席內容官何麗全<br />\n<br />\n呢個職位名都幾新穎吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582cd3993d26026428f565ad11fb8b057f45bd3b","tid":762062,"uid":92603,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"宜家睇亞視係咪要錢？"},{"pid":"ad34c6057633131537551f40f244c22eef3acdaa","tid":762062,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9605a1a86a8e2164e2f7e3305bd2dc7b25bf2253","tid":762062,"uid":1848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:01:11.000Z","msg":"首席內容官何麗全<br />\n<br />\n呢個職位名都幾新穎吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:13:37.000Z","msg":"支那餘孽陰魂不散<br />\n<br />\n何麗全同吳雨，唉好心收山啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1734977d81147d77a32d2fc696bb73309e6dbb7b","tid":762062,"uid":8883,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"見到亞視以為回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚記得左佢番生"},{"pid":"58cc583548b24c70bf1c5a38de9bcc58e07b39bd","tid":762062,"uid":47674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T06:29:09.000Z","msg":"有人睇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src